// ▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄
       

#include <behaviors.dtsi>
#include <dt-bindings/zmk/keys.h>
#include <dt-bindings/zmk/bt.h>
#include <dt-bindings/zmk/outputs.h>

#define BASE 0
#define NAV  1
#define SYM  2
#define ADJ  3
#define TVP1 4
#define TVP2 5

&mt {
  quick-tap-ms = <100>;
  global-quick-tap;
  flavor = "tap-preferred";
  tapping-term-ms = <170>;
};

/ {
     behaviors {
            ht_minus: hold_tap_minus {
                compatible = "zmk,behavior-hold-tap";
                label = "HOLD_TAP_MINUS";
                #binding-cells = <2>;
                tapping-term-ms = <200>;
                quick-tap-ms = <0>;
                flavor = "tap-preferred";
                bindings = <&kp>, <&kp>;
            };
            ht_comma: hold_tap_comma {
                compatible = "zmk,behavior-hold-tap";
                label = "HOLD_TAP_COMMA";
                #binding-cells = <2>;
                tapping-term-ms = <200>;
                quick-tap-ms = <0>;
                flavor = "tap-preferred";
                bindings = <&kp>, <&kp>;
            };
            ht_semi: hold_tap_semi {
                compatible = "zmk,behavior-hold-tap";
                label = "HOLD_TAP_SEMI";
                #binding-cells = <2>;
                tapping-term-ms = <200>;
                quick-tap-ms = <0>;
                flavor = "tap-preferred";
                bindings = <&kp>, <&kp>;
            };
            ht_slash: hold_tap_slash {
                compatible = "zmk,behavior-hold-tap";
                label = "HOLD_TAP_SLASH";
                #binding-cells = <2>;
                tapping-term-ms = <200>;
                quick-tap-ms = <0>;
                flavor = "tap-preferred";
                bindings = <&kp>, <&kp>;
            };
            ht_o: hold_tap_o {
                compatible = "zmk,behavior-hold-tap";
                label = "HOLD_TAP_O";
                #binding-cells = <2>;
                tapping-term-ms = <200>;
                quick-tap-ms = <0>;
                flavor = "tap-preferred";
                bindings = <&kp>, <&kp>;
            };
            ht_p: hold_tap_p {
                compatible = "zmk,behavior-hold-tap";
                label = "HOLD_TAP_P";
                #binding-cells = <2>;
                tapping-term-ms = <200>;
                quick-tap-ms = <0>;
                flavor = "tap-preferred";
                bindings = <&kp>, <&kp>;
            };
            ht_n1: hold_tap_n1 {
                compatible = "zmk,behavior-hold-tap";
                label = "HOLD_TAP_N1";
                #binding-cells = <2>;
                tapping-term-ms = <200>;
                quick-tap-ms = <0>;
                flavor = "tap-preferred";
                bindings = <&kp>, <&kp>;
            };
            ht_n2: hold_tap_n2 {
                compatible = "zmk,behavior-hold-tap";
                label = "HOLD_TAP_N2";
                #binding-cells = <2>;
                tapping-term-ms = <200>;
                quick-tap-ms = <0>;
                flavor = "tap-preferred";
                bindings = <&kp>, <&kp>;
            };
            ht_n3: hold_tap_n3 {
                compatible = "zmk,behavior-hold-tap";
                label = "HOLD_TAP_N3";
                #binding-cells = <2>;
                tapping-term-ms = <200>;
                quick-tap-ms = <0>;
                flavor = "tap-preferred";
                bindings = <&kp>, <&kp>;
            };
            ht_n4: hold_tap_n4 {
                compatible = "zmk,behavior-hold-tap";
                label = "HOLD_TAP_N4";
                #binding-cells = <2>;
                tapping-term-ms = <200>;
                quick-tap-ms = <0>;
                flavor = "tap-preferred";
                bindings = <&kp>, <&kp>;
            };
            ht_n5: hold_tap_n5 {
                compatible = "zmk,behavior-hold-tap";
                label = "HOLD_TAP_N5";
                #binding-cells = <2>;
                tapping-term-ms = <200>;
                quick-tap-ms = <0>;
                flavor = "tap-preferred";
                bindings = <&kp>, <&kp>;
            };
            ht_n6: hold_tap_n6 {
                compatible = "zmk,behavior-hold-tap";
                label = "HOLD_TAP_N6";
                #binding-cells = <2>;
                tapping-term-ms = <200>;
                quick-tap-ms = <0>;
                flavor = "tap-preferred";
                bindings = <&kp>, <&kp>;
            };
            ht_n7: hold_tap_n7 {
                compatible = "zmk,behavior-hold-tap";
                label = "HOLD_TAP_N7";
                #binding-cells = <2>;
                tapping-term-ms = <200>;
                quick-tap-ms = <0>;
                flavor = "tap-preferred";
                bindings = <&kp>, <&kp>;
            };
            ht_n8: hold_tap_n8 {
                compatible = "zmk,behavior-hold-tap";
                label = "HOLD_TAP_N8";
                #binding-cells = <2>;
                tapping-term-ms = <200>;
                quick-tap-ms = <0>;
                flavor = "tap-preferred";
                bindings = <&kp>, <&kp>;
            };
            ht_q: hold_tap_q {
                compatible = "zmk,behavior-hold-tap";
                label = "HOLD_TAP_Q";
                #binding-cells = <2>;
                tapping-term-ms = <200>;
                quick-tap-ms = <0>;
                flavor = "tap-preferred";
                bindings = <&mo>, <&kp>;
            };
     };

     combos {
            compatible = "zmk,combos";
            combo_esc {
                timeout-ms = <50>;
                key-positions = <0 1>;
                bindings = <&kp ESC>;
            };
            combo_tvp {
                timeout-ms = <100>;
                key-positions = <11 12 13>;
                bindings = <&tog TVP1>;
            };
    };

    macros {
        gif: gif {
            label = "giphy";
            compatible = "zmk,behavior-macro";
            #binding-cells = <0>;
            bindings
                = <&macro_press &kp LSHFT>
                , <&macro_tap &kp N2>
                , <&macro_release &kp LSHFT>
                , <&macro_tap &kp G &kp I &kp F>
                ;
        };
    };

        keymap {
                compatible = "zmk,keymap";
// ▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄

                base_layer {
// ┏━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┓
label= "BASE"                              ;
// ┗━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┛
//             ┏━━━━━━━━━━━┳━━━━━━━━━━━┳━━━━━━━━━━━┳━━━━━━━━━━━┳━━━━━━━━━━━┓   ┏━━━━━━━━━━━┳━━━━━━━━━━━┳━━━━━━━━━━━┳━━━━━━━━━━━┳━━━━━━━━━━━┓
//             ┃     Q     ┃     W     ┃     E     ┃     R     ┃     T     ┃   ┃     Y     ┃     U     ┃     I     ┃     O     ┃     P     ┃
//             ┣━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━┫   ┣━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━┫
//             ┃     A     ┃     S     ┃     D     ┃     F     ┃     G     ┃   ┃     H     ┃     J     ┃     K     ┃     L     ┃     ;     ┃
// ┏━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━┫   ┣━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━┓
// ┃   SHIFT   ┃     Z     ┃     X     ┃     C     ┃     V     ┃     B     ┃   ┃     N     ┃     M     ┃     ,     ┃     .     ┃     /     ┃   SHIFT   ┃
// ┗━━━━━━━━━━━┻━━━━━━━━━━━┻━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━┫   ┣━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━┻━━━━━━━━━━━┻━━━━━━━━━━━┛
//                                     ┃   CTRL    ┃   BSPC    ┃    CMD    ┃   ┃   ENTER   ┃    SPC    ┃   NAVI    ┃
//                                     ┃           ┃  (→NAV)   ┃   (GUI)   ┃   ┃           ┃           ┃  (→NAV)   ┃
//                                     ┗━━━━━━━━━━━┻━━━━━━━━━━━┻━━━━━━━━━━━┛   ┗━━━━━━━━━━━┻━━━━━━━━━━━┻━━━━━━━━━━━┛
 bindings = <
// ╷           ╷           ╷           ╷           ╷           ╷           ╷   ╷           ╷           ╷           ╷           ╷           ╷           ╷

                &ht_q NAV Q &kp W       &kp E       &kp R       &kp T           &kp Y       &kp U       &kp I       &ht_o PIPE O       &ht_p BSLH P
                &kp A       &kp S       &kp D       &kp F       &kp G           &kp H       &kp J       &kp K       &kp L       &ht_semi DQT SEMI
    &kp LSHFT   &kp Z       &kp X       &kp C       &kp V       &kp B           &kp N       &kp M       &kp COMMA   &kp DOT     &ht_slash SQT FSLH    &kp RSHFT
                                        &kp LCTRL   &kp BSPC    &kp LGUI        &kp RET   &kp SPACE   &mo NAV
                        >;
                };

// ▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄


                nav_layer {
// ┏━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┓
label= "NAVI"                              ;
// ┗━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┛
//             ┏━━━━━━━━━━━┳━━━━━━━━━━━┳━━━━━━━━━━━┳━━━━━━━━━━━┳━━━━━━━━━━━┓   ┏━━━━━━━━━━━┳━━━━━━━━━━━┳━━━━━━━━━━━┳━━━━━━━━━━━┳━━━━━━━━━━━┓
//             ┃    ESC    ┃           ┃     UP    ┃           ┃     {     ┃   ┃     }     ┃     7     ┃     8     ┃     9     ┃     +     ┃
//             ┣━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━┫   ┣━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━┫
//             ┃    TAB    ┃   LEFT    ┃    DOWN   ┃   RIGHT   ┃     [     ┃   ┃     ]     ┃     4     ┃     5     ┃     6     ┃     -     ┃
// ┏━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━┫   ┣━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━┓
// ┃   SHIFT   ┃    DEL    ┃   P UP    ┃  C LOCK   ┃  P DOWN   ┃     (     ┃   ┃     )     ┃     1     ┃     2     ┃     3     ┃     *     ┃     =     ┃
// ┗━━━━━━━━━━━┻━━━━━━━━━━━┻━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━┫   ┣━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━┻━━━━━━━━━━━┻━━━━━━━━━━━┛
//                                     ┃    ADJ    ┃   BSPC    ┃    CMD    ┃   ┃           ┃     0     ┃           ┃
//                                     ┗━━━━━━━━━━━┻━━━━━━━━━━━┻━━━━━━━━━━━┛   ┗━━━━━━━━━━━┻━━━━━━━━━━━┻━━━━━━━━━━━┛
 bindings = <
// ╷           ╷           ╷           ╷           ╷           ╷           ╷   ╷           ╷           ╷           ╷           ╷           ╷           ╷

                &kp ESC     &trans      &kp UP      &trans      &kp LBRC        &kp RBRC    &ht_n7 AMPS KP_N7   &ht_n8 TILDE KP_N8   &kp KP_N9   &kp KP_PLUS
                &kp TAB     &kp LEFT    &kp DOWN    &kp RIGHT   &kp LBKT        &kp RBKT    &ht_n4 DLLR KP_N4   &ht_n5 PRCNT KP_N5   &ht_n6 CARET KP_N6   &ht_minus UNDER KP_MINUS
    &kp LSHFT   &kp DEL     &kp PG_UP   &kp CAPS    &kp PG_DN   &kp LPAR        &kp RPAR    &ht_n1 EXCL KP_N1   &ht_n2 AT KP_N2   &ht_n3 HASH KP_N3   &kp KP_MULTIPLY &kp EQUAL
                                        &mo ADJ     &trans      &trans          &trans      &kp KP_N0   &trans      
                        >;
                };

// ▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄


                sim_layer {
// ┏━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┓
label= "SYM"                               ;
// ┗━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┛
//             ┏━━━━━━━━━━━┳━━━━━━━━━━━┳━━━━━━━━━━━┳━━━━━━━━━━━┳━━━━━━━━━━━┓   ┏━━━━━━━━━━━┳━━━━━━━━━━━┳━━━━━━━━━━━┳━━━━━━━━━━━┳━━━━━━━━━━━┓
//             ┃     !     ┃     @     ┃     #     ┃     $     ┃     %     ┃   ┃     ˆ     ┃     &     ┃     Ü     ┃     '     ┃     "     ┃
//             ┣━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━┫   ┣━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━┫
//             ┃     Ä     ┃           ┃    SZ     ┃           ┃           ┃   ┃   MUTE    ┃   YEN     ┃   EURO    ┃  POUND    ┃     Ö     ┃
// ┏━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━┫   ┣━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━┓
// ┃           ┃  EMAIL1   ┃  EMAIL2   ┃           ┃           ┃           ┃   ┃   VOL-    ┃   VOL+    ┃   LAST    ┃   NEXT    ┃     \     ┃           ┃
// ┗━━━━━━━━━━━┻━━━━━━━━━━━┻━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━┫   ┣━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━╋━━━━━━━━━━━┻━━━━━━━━━━━┻━━━━━━━━━━━┛
//                                     ┃           ┃    GIF    ┃    ADJ    ┃   ┃           ┃    SPC    ┃           ┃
//                                     ┗━━━━━━━━━━━┻━━━━━━━━━━━┻━━━━━━━━━━━┛   ┗━━━━━━━━━━━┻━━━━━━━━━━━┻━━━━━━━━━━━┛
 bindings = <
// ╷           ╷           ╷           ╷           ╷           ╷           ╷   ╷           ╷           ╷           ╷           ╷           ╷           ╷

                &kp EXCL    &kp AT      &kp HASH    &kp DLLR    &kp PRCNT       &kp CARET   &kp AMPS    &kp RA(U)   &kp SQT     &kp DQT       
                &kp RA(A)   &trans      &kp RA(S)   &trans      &trans          &kp C_MUTE  &kp LS(RA(N4)) &kp RA(N5) &kp RA(N4)   &kp RA(O) 
    &trans      &kp RA(F18) &kp RA(F19) &trans      &trans      &trans          &kp C_VOL_DN &kp C_VOL_UP &kp C_PREV &kp C_NEXT  &kp BSLH   &trans         
                                        &trans      &gif        &mo ADJ         &trans      &kp C_PP    &trans      
                        >;
                };

// ▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄▄


                adjust_layer {
// ┏━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┓
label= "ADJ"                               ;
// ┗━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━━┛
